data.description: Looking for a fantastic location? Look no further than this stunning home on Carrie Circle cul-de-sac, perfect for families! The main level and stairs boast gorgeous wood flooring and tile, while the newer master bedroom features the same, as well as six-panel doors throughout the house. The second floor is home to four bedrooms, including a private master suite that is separate from the other three bedrooms, as well as two and a half baths and two dining areas. Step out onto the great deck to enjoy a picturesque view of the backyard. The house also comes with new appliances, underground dog fencing, and window treatments. The full basement offers additional storage space, or the potential to finish it as you see fit. The attached three-car garage and shed provide ample storage space for all your toys! This fantastic property spans over half an acre in town, and is conveniently located just down the road from Tainter Elementary, the Rice Lake splash pad, and soccer fields.
